Package org.neo4j.kernel.impl.util.watcher

Class DefaultFileSystemWatcherService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.util.watcher.DefaultFileSystemWatcherService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FileSystemWatcherService, Lifecycle
    public class DefaultFileSystemWatcherService
extends Object
implements FileSystemWatcherService
    Factory used for construction of proper adaptor for available FileWatcher. In case if silent matcher is used dummy adapter will be used, otherwise will use default wrapper that will bind monitoring cycles to corresponding lifecycle phases.
